%section.hero#hero
  .container
    .row
      .title.text-center
        Find your perfect mover
      = form_tag movers_path, method: :get do
        = text_field_tag :from, 'Boulder', readonly: true, data: {label: "From:"}
        = text_field_tag :to, nil, placeholder: 'To', autofocus: true, data: {label: "To:"}
        = submit_tag :discover, value: 'Discover', name: nil, class: "btn-discover"
%section.row
  .col-xs-12.col-md-10.col-md-offset-1.text-center
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-md-4.explainer
      %h2 Transparency
      %p.lead
        Transparency is about keeping you informed of all possible options you might want at every step of the process.
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-md-4.explainer
      %h2 Pricing
      %p.lead
        Pricing is at our core, because you should know exactly what you're signing up for and expected to pay at the end.
    .col-xs-12.col-sm-4.col-md-4.explainer
      %h2 Convenience
      %p.lead
        Convenience and Control go hand-in-hand. You should be able to communicate things that you need, whether through phone/email/text/carrier-pigeon

:javascript
  $(document).ready(function(){
    $('#hero input').floatlabel({
      slideInput: false,
      paddingOffset: "5px",
      labelStartTop: '30px',
      labelEndTop: '0px'
    });
  });
